data.description: Enter to a country kitchen-dining area which includes an island and window seats. The washer and dryer are here, so no running up and down stairs to put in a load of wash while cooking. The bathroom sits off the living room and was remodeled in 2022. All bedrooms are upstairs and are carpeted, the primary bedroom has cathedral ceiling. This three bedroom home sits on over 4 acres of land. Structures on the property include a shed, workshop, pool with deck, and paved sitting area. Updates include bathroom remodel (2022), metal roof (2023) and porch/deck 2022. 24 hour notice is appreciated, the house is available to show 10am to 7pm. 2023-11-03
